{"tid":649653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook連Tinder嗰份都撈埋","createTime":"2018-05-01T17:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T08:39:55.000Z","uid":57369,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"61372ff1781353bb7e6904a6de953e9556aa397d","tid":649653,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T17:38:17.000Z","msg":"Facebook is adding a dating layer to its main mobile app, CEO Mark Zuckerberg announced today during the company&rsquo;s F8 developers conference keynote in San Jose, California. The features are a long time coming for the 14-year-old social network, which has allowed users to broadcast whether they&rsquo;re single or in a relationship since it first went live in February 2004.<br />\n<br />\nThe move will likely transform Facebook, with its more than 2.2 billion monthly active users, into a major competitor of Match Group, which owns and operates mobile dating app Tinder and popular dating platform OkCupid.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;This is going to be for building real, long-term relationships &mdash; not just for hookups,&rdquo; Zuckerberg joked onstage. He added that it&rsquo;s going to be within the main Facebook app, but it will be completely optional and opt-in only. &ldquo;We have designed this with privacy and safety in mind from the beginning. Your friends aren&rsquo;t going to see your profile, and you&rsquo;re only going to be suggested to people who are not your friends.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nMatch Group&rsquo;s stock plummeted by nearly 10 percent as soon as the news was announced.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2018/5/1/17307782/facebook-tinder-dating-app-f8-match-okcupid\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2018%2F5%2F1%2F17307782%2Ffacebook-tinder-dating-app-f8-match-okcupid&d=vrCOODsnyhR98tITzBF8ViwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=e6de463c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2018/5/1/17307782/facebook-tinder-dating-app-f8-match-okcupid</a>"},{"pid":"70c721818dc875240a2388ecd8e03de9f09f9f51","tid":649653,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T19:24:26.000Z","msg":"百抄公司"},{"pid":"fd31456946e8ee593dfb412dac147626f3df8a2d","tid":649653,"uid":123264,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"70c721818dc875240a2388ecd8e03de9f09f9f51","tid":649653,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T19:24:26.000Z","msg":"百抄公司"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T19:48:18.000Z","msg":"zuc根本係支那種<br />\n偷人資料,抄人公司發展模式,刷權貴鞋<br />\n連身高都係支那種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69e10bfa949cfe6d027a01876317f703f2daa3e","tid":649653,"uid":123264,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"fd31456946e8ee593dfb412dac147626f3df8a2d","tid":649653,"uid":123264,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"70c721818dc875240a2388ecd8e03de9f09f9f51","tid":649653,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T19:24:26.000Z","msg":"百抄公司"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T19:48:18.000Z","msg":"zuc根本係支那種<br />\n偷人資料,抄人公司發展模式,刷權貴鞋<br />\n連身高都係支那種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T19:48:37.000Z","msg":"個7到核爆既老婆都係支那種<br />\n呢條友唔生係支那真係可惜"},{"pid":"f3379cf6eec547e8a628d48ee8a87c13475f7a4d","tid":649653,"uid":176935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T19:56:13.000Z","msg":"咁以為自己男女朋友可以無聲無色用facebook識人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82446e70ba422764938f285c43edcd25a5d9852a","tid":649653,"uid":176935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T19:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁以後自己男女朋友可以無聲無色用facebook識人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"321be7aef2f53355c382244b7d263fea8692dfbd","tid":649653,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd3145